# Prettier's MDX printer collapses fenced code blocks nested inside JSX (e.g.
# <Tab>```bash ... ```</Tab>) onto a single line, which breaks Fumadocs
# rendering. There is no option to disable this. MDX content is hand-authored,
# so keep it out of Prettier entirely.
docs/content/**/*.mdx
